data.description: Beautiful 4 SIDE CUSTOM MADE brick home!   This charming home invites you to experience a perfect blend of warmth and character. From the moment you step through the door, you'll be captivated by the thoughtful design.      The grand entrance sets the tone, welcoming you with a sense of elegance. The formal living and dining rooms make an ideal space for entertaining and creating lasting memories. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, where culinary dreams come true. Adorned with elegant granite countertops, a tasteful tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances, it's a haven for both aspiring chefs and casual entertainers alike. The backyard boasts a massive patio, providing the ideal setting for gatherings, barbecues, or simply unwinding in complete privacy.  Each offering ample space for rest and relaxation. Escape to the finished basement—a multifunctional haven featuring office spaces, an additional family room, an entertainment area, and a cozy theatre space. The possibilities are endless for creating the perfect retreat tailored to your lifestyle. This home is a MUST-SEE!     This 6 HUGE bedrooms, 5.5 bath home has everything you could imagine! ALL ROOMS ARE HUGE and very suitable for big family or extended family.  HUGE primary bedroom suite has private bathroom with separate tub/shower and large closet. Three more well sized bedrooms make up this home!!   Flat and grassy front yard and well maintained backyard makes IDEAL place for farming or any other agricultural dream you have! Located in the esteemed region of Stockbridge located near plenty of grocery stores, shopping, schools and more!
